---
title: Pork Chop with Braised Cabbage, Potato Wedges and Cranberry and Pistachio Jam
description: This tasty recipe is great for the chilly weeks leading up to Christmas; it’s warm and hearty and the pistachio and cranberry jam adds a beautiful sweet flavour that lifts the dish. The jam is a great accompaniment
to roasted meats such as pork, turkey and chicken and would fit in perfectly with a Christmas roast. Practice makes perfect...
